            , was indicted for the <rs id="t17170227-33-off157" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17170227-33-off157" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17170227-33-off157" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               Murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17170227-33-victim198" type="victimName">
                           Judith 
                           Spoonly 
                        <interp inst="t17170227-33-victim198" type="surname" value="Spoonly"></interp>
